President Obama has announced his intent to nominate Mark T. Nethery for the position of Member of the Board of Trustees of the Morris K. Udall and Stewart L. Udall Foundation. Nethery is the Founder and Owner of Bluegrass Game Calls, LLC, and also works as a freelance outdoor writer. He previously served as Chief Operations Officer for the John Conti Coffee Company and as a Restaurant Industry Liaison for the International Coffee Organization. Nethery has also held various positions in the Kentucky Restaurant Association and is currently serving as President of the League of KY Sportsmen.